    <p>
      <font size="1" face="Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000">In Canary, remember that to enable all of the latest JavaScript experiments you should navigate to</font><font face="Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000">&#160;</font><code style="word-spacing: 0px; text-align: start; padding-bottom: 1px; color: black; white-space: normal; padding-right: 3px; font-weight: normal; font-variant: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 233, 204); padding-left: 3px; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 1px; font-style: normal; font-size: 1em"><font size="1em" color="black">chrome:flags</font></code><font face="Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000">&#160;</font><font size="1" face="Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000">and use the 'Enable Experimental JavaScript' option. </font><font face="Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000">ES.next features can be experimented with using Google's</font><a style="font-size: 15px; border-left-width: 0px; color: rgb(217, 51, 21); text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 25.84000015258789px; border-bottom-style: none; margin-right: 0px; font-variant: normal; border-right-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: start; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; white-space: normal; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-style: none; font-weight: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-style: normal; padding-top: 0px; border-right-style: none; word-spacing: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)" href="https://code.google.com/p/traceur-compiler/"><font size="15px" face="Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="rgb(217, 51, 21)">Traceur</font></a><font face="Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif