mal; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; display: inline !important; text-align: start; white-space: normal; float: none; font-weight: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">the proposal.</span></font>
